 \file   segway_faultlog_parser

 \brief  Parses the faultlog into human readable form via html. Faultlog will
         provide details to diagnose issues to the component level for rapid service.
         Only valid for a present SI release; if you have an old release
         contact rmp@stanleyinnovation.com to get upgrade details.

